{"id":16,"parent_id":7,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":16,"title":"1 Nephi 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","Nephi makes two sets of records—Each is called the plates of Nephi—The larger plates contain a secular history; the smaller ones deal primarily with sacred things. About 600–592",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.1","order":"05.12.009.925"},["b","1"],"And all these things did my father see, and hear, and speak, as he dwelt in a tent, in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"valley of Lemuel"],", and also a great many more things, which cannot be written upon these plates."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.2","order":"05.12.009.926"},["b","2"],"And now, as I have spoken concerning these plates, behold they are not the plates upon which I make a full account of the history of my people; for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"plates"],"upon which I make a full account of my people I have given the name of Nephi; wherefore, they are called the plates of Nephi, after mine own name; and these plates also are called the plates of Nephi."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.3","order":"05.12.009.927"},["b","3"],"Nevertheless, I have received a commandment of the Lord that I should make these plates, for the special",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"purpose"],"that there should be an account engraven of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"ministry"],"of my people."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.4","order":"05.12.009.928"},["b","4"],"Upon the other plates should be engraven an account of the reign of the kings, and the wars and contentions of my people; wherefore these plates are for the more part of the ministry; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"other plates"],"are for the more part of the reign of the kings and the wars and contentions of my people."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.5","order":"05.12.009.929"},["b","5"],"Wherefore, the Lord hath commanded me to make these plates for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wise"],"purpose in him, which purpose I know not."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.6","order":"05.12.009.930"},["b","6"],"But the Lord",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"knoweth"],"all things from the beginning; wherefore, he prepareth a way to accomplish all his works among the children of men; for behold, he hath all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"power"],"unto the fulfilling of all his words. And thus it is. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.1a","order":"05.12.009.931"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.6.4-6,8,14-15"},"1 Ne. 2:6 (4–6, 8, 14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.6.6,12"},"16:6 (6, 12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.2a","order":"05.12.009.933"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"the full account is on larger plates; the special account of his ministry is on the smaller plates of Nephi. See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.13-14"},"Jacob 3:13–14"],". See also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.17.16-17"},"1 Ne. 1:17 (16–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/6.1"},"6:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.1"},"10:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.2,4"},"19:2, 4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.1"},"Omni 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.3.2-11"},"W of M 1:3 (2–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.38.38-40"},"D&C 10:38 (38–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.3a","order":"05.12.009.935"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.19"},"D&C 3:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.3b","order":"05.12.009.937"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/6.3"},"1 Ne. 6:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.4a","order":"05.12.009.939"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.14"},"2 Ne. 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.33.29-33"},"5:33 (29–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/1.3.2-4"},"Jacob 1:3 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jarom/1.14"},"Jarom 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.18"},"Omni 1:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.10"},"W of M 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.5a","order":"05.12.009.941"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.3"},"1 Ne. 19:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.7"},"W of M 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.14.2,12,14"},"Alma 37:14 (2, 12, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.6a","order":"05.12.009.943"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48.3.3-7"},"Isa. 48:3 (3–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.6,35"},"Moses 1:6, 35"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-foreknowledge-of"},"TG God, Foreknowledge of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-intelligence-of"},"God, Intelligence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.6b","order":"05.12.009.945"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18"},"Matt. 28:18"],"."]]}
